# Informations how to create the remote event server for MBS on Linux
# last update: 18.12.2001, Horst Goeringer
########################################################################

V20: 18.12.2001: built events of any length from fragments
     

To create and run the remote event server for MBS, perform the following 
steps:

(1) execute make file to create the executable mrevserv:

    make -f MRevServ.make

(2) start executable

    mrevserv daq-node 6002 options

For more information and for information on the ROOT event client for
MBS see

http://www-aix.gsi.de/~goeri/mbsnew/online.html

